==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Ir
<hw>Ir</hw> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Chem.)</fld> <def>The chemical symbol
for iridium, a metallic element of the platinum group. It has atomic
number 77 and an atomic weight of 192.22.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> iridium.</syn>⟦br⟧
[<source>WordNet 1.5</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Ir-</ent>⟦br⟧

==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Ir-
<hw>Ir-</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <def>A form of the prefix <xex>in</xex>-. See
<er>In-</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>IRA</ent>⟦br⟧
